title: Best Bits of the Week with Morgan2 - What You Didn't Hear About Raymundo's Brotox (Week of 4/5)
itunes:title: Best Bits of the Week with Morgan2 - What You Didn't Hear About Raymundo's Brotox (Week of 4/5)
description:
This edition of the podcast features behind the scenes from show members and moments that happened after we turned off the microphones. Morgan2 brings on Raymundo to talk about why he got botox aka 'brotox'. We also get to know a little bit more about Raymundo and what's really going on inside his brain.
